---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs TrustPulse — Real testimonials vs FOMO popups | SocialProof" description="TrustPulse shows 'someone just bought' popups. SocialProof collects and displays real customer testimonials. See which builds more lasting trust." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/trustpulse">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .savings-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .insight-box { background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3.5rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .bottom-cta a { background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media(max-width:600px) { .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/for">Solutions</a>
    <a href="/vs">Comparisons</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-nav">Try Free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <span class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs TrustPulse</span>
  <h1>FOMO popups fade.<br/><span>Real testimonials last.</span></h1>
  <p>TrustPulse shows visitors real-time activity popups ("Sarah from Denver just purchased!"). SocialProof collects and displays actual customer words — specific, personal, persuasive. Both build trust, but in very different ways.</p>
  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch"><div class="price">Free</div><div class="label">SocialProof to start</div></div>
    <div class="item other"><div class="price">$5+</div><div class="label">TrustPulse per month</div></div>
  </div>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="hero-cta">Start free with SocialProof →</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Two different types of social proof</h2>
  <p>TrustPulse is a <strong>FOMO tool</strong> — it shows real-time notifications about recent actions on your site to create urgency. It works well for e-commerce stores with active traffic. But it requires visitors to already be on your site, and the effect diminishes when visitors see the same popup pattern repeatedly.</p>
  <p>SocialProof is a <strong>testimonial platform</strong> — it helps you collect, manage, and embed written testimonials from real customers. Testimonials answer the question "will this work for me?" with specific, relatable stories from people like the visitor.</p>

  <div class="insight-box">
    <strong>Key insight:</strong> FOMO notifications work best at the bottom of the funnel (they push hesitant buyers to convert). Testimonials work throughout the funnel — they build trust on first visit, during comparison, and at checkout.
  </div>

  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>SocialProof</th><th>TrustPulse</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Starting price</td><td class="yes">Free forever (1 widget)</td><td class="no">$5/mo (very limited)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Collects written testimonials</td><td class="yes">Yes — core feature</td><td class="no">No</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Real-time activity popups</td><td class="no">No</td><td class="yes">Yes — core feature</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Works with low traffic sites</td><td class="yes">Yes — testimonials always show</td><td class="no">No (needs traffic to show activity)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Works for service businesses</td><td class="yes">Yes</td><td class="partial">Limited (no "purchases")</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Content stays evergreen</td><td class="yes">Yes — testimonials don't expire</td><td class="no">No — stale when traffic drops</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Google-indexable content</td><td class="yes">Yes (embedded testimonials)</td><td class="no">No (JS popups)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Embed on any page</td><td class="yes">Yes</td><td class="yes">Yes</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✅ Choose SocialProof if…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You're a service business, coach, or consultant</li>
        <li>Your site has moderate or inconsistent traffic</li>
        <li>You want testimonials that work without daily visitors</li>
        <li>You need evergreen trust signals that don't go stale</li>
        <li>You want to start free with no credit card</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Consider TrustPulse if…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You have a high-traffic e-commerce store</li>
        <li>You want urgency-based conversion nudges</li>
        <li>You already have testimonials elsewhere and need FOMO layer</li>
        <li>You're already in the OptinMonster ecosystem</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="savings-box">
    <h3>💡 Use both? Here's the overlap</h3>
    <p>Some businesses use FOMO notification tools and testimonial platforms together. But if you're choosing one: for service businesses and sites with modest traffic, testimonials deliver more consistent value. TrustPulse is a tactic. Testimonials are a strategy.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="bottom-cta">
    <h2>Build trust that doesn't expire.</h2>
    <p>Collect real testimonials, approve them, embed them anywhere. Works for any business size — free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup">Get started free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/vs" style="color:#888">More comparisons</a> · <a href="/" style="color:#888">Home</a></p>
</footer>
</Base>
